article_text:
Double Take 'Toons: Obamacare: Home-Stretchers?

To meet HHS's goal, almost two million Americans will have to buy a health plan by March 31. Eric Allie doubts it will happen, while Matt Weurker thinks exaggerations about Obamacare haven't helped.

toggle caption Eric Allie
